    • Constructor Detail

      • WordToFoConverter

        public WordToFoConverter(org.w3c.dom.Document document)
        Creates new instance of WordToFoConverter. Can be used for output several HWPFDocuments into single FO document.(创建WordToFoEditor的新实例。可用于将多个HWPFDoc输出到单个FO文档中。)
        Parameters:
        document - XML DOM Document used as XSL FO document. Shall support namespaces(document -用作XSL FO文档的XML DOM文档。应支持命名空间)

      • main

        public static void main(java.lang.String[] args)
                 throws java.lang.Exception
        Java main() interface to interact with WordToFoConverter

        Usage: WordToFoConverter infile outfile

        Where infile is an input .doc file ( Word 97-2007) which will be rendered as XSL-FO into outfile        (Java main（）接口，用于与WordToFoConverter交互使用：WordToFoConverter infile outfile其中infile是输入.Doc文件（Word 97-2007），将作为XSL-FO呈现到outfile中)
        Throws:
        java.lang.Exception(java.lang.Exception)

      • processBookmarks

        protected void processBookmarks(HWPFDocumentCore wordDocument,
                                org.w3c.dom.Element currentBlock,
                                Range range,
                                int currentTableLevel,
                                java.util.List<Bookmark> rangeBookmarks)
        Description copied from class: AbstractWordConverter
        Wrap range into bookmark(s) and process it. All bookmarks have starts equal to range start and ends equal to range end. Usually it's only one bookmark.(将范围包装到书签中并对其进行处理。所有书签的start等于range start，end等于range end。通常只有一个书签。)
        Specified by:
